here what we are doing is we are parting our single c files into many different files 
to do so we have the following structure 


project contains one single file main.c and two folders includes and src
in includes we have headers 
in src we have source code


in C to start a header write 
#ifndef HEADER_NAME_INCAPS_H
#define HEADER_NAME_INCAPS_H
// what ever function you want only names
#endif

in .C files include the header and write the function
import the headers in the main.c do not need relative paths take care during compling

to compile write as follow gcc -I ./includes src/*.cpp -o fileName
